          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Ankle and foot fractures
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Hip and femur fractures
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Pediatric and sports-related fractures
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Advanced Orthopaedic Trauma Care in Hyderabad
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Depending on the severity of the fracture, treatment may involve
          casting, splinting, or surgical fixation using plates, screws, or rods.
          Dr. Karthik Manchala ensures precise diagnosis and structured follow-up
          care for optimal recovery.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Why Choose Dr. Karthik Manchala for Fracture Treatment?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          With over 12 years of orthopaedic experience, Dr. Karthik Manchala
          is known for his expertise in fracture management and trauma care.
          Patients from Manikonda, Alkapur Township, Puppalaguda, Narsingi,
          and nearby Hyderabad areas trust his compassionate and precise approach.
        </p>

      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Booking */}
    <BookingForm client:load />

    <Footer client:load />
